FAQs

frequently asked questions

We’re excited to hear from you! Whether you have a question

What is an AI software developer?

An AI software developer integrates artificial intelligence capabilities into software applications, embedding AI algorithms and logic within project deliverables as part of IT initiatives.

What is the salary of an AI engineer?

In India, the salary for an AI Engineer varies from 3.0 Lakhs to 20.0 Lakhs, averaging around 7.2 Lakhs annually. This information is derived from 573 recent salary reports from AI Engineers.

How AI can be used in software development?

The utilization of AI in software development is highlighted in the Google Cloud Blog. AI plays a pivotal role in automating monotonous tasks like code reviews, testing, and debugging. This not only reduces developers’ workload but also enables them to channel their efforts toward creative and significant endeavors.

Is AI software as a service?

AI as a Service follows the Software as a Service model, where external companies provide their offerings to users through a subscription. In this context, AI as a Service enables users to access and leverage AI technology for their benefit.

Is artificial intelligence part of software development?

Certainly, artificial intelligence is integrated into the realm of software development. It proves particularly valuable in automating monotonous and routine assignments across various sectors. Regardless of the industry, AI operates based on specific instructions or predefined guidelines. As a result, within the context of software development, AI assumes responsibility for repetitive duties, consequently leading to an evolution in the roles of developers.
